lead_paragraph: If a standout movie is guaranteed by a stellar cast, then the Masters is shaping up as one of the best in recent memory with all of the game's leading players having produced superb form over the past three months.

headline.print_headline: Day Heads Stellar Cast to Set Up a Masters Special
